children.name: Outcome 1.1 - Institutions in Jordan at national and local levels are more responsive, inclusive, accountable, transparent and resilient.
Output 1.1.1 - Strengthening Institutions to improve performance: National and local public institutions are better able to perform their core functions giving attention to needs of vulnerable groups
